<figureCitation box="[750,765,1785,1811]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[189,232,1889,1915]" captionTargetBox="[253,1334,292,1806]" captionTargetId="figure@9.[228,1359,267,1833]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 4. Adult habitus. A–B. D. seguyi Smart, 1945 (MNHN). A. ♂. B. ♀. C–D. D. malagassya Tsacas &amp; Rafael, 1982 (MNHN). C. ♂. D. ♀. E–F. D. curta Chassagnard &amp; Tsacas, 1997 (MNHN). E. ♂. F. ♀. G–H. D. chocolata Yassin &amp; David sp. nov. (MNHN). G. ♂. H. ♀. Only dark morphs of females of species with female-limited color dimorphism are shown. Scale bar = 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3251577/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">4</figureCitation>
